        <mxCell id="footer-slas" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#1E2761;fontSize=10;fontStyle=0;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;" value="KEY SLAs&#xa;&#xa;• Ingestion Latency (Streaming): &lt; 5 min&#xa;• Prediction Latency (P95): &lt; 150 ms&#xa;• Agent Screen Lookup: &lt; 50 ms (DDB)&#xa;• Pipeline Availability: 99.9%&#xa;• Model Availability (Endpoint): 99.95%" vertex="1">
