        <mxCell id="footer-ref" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFDE7;strokeColor=#F57F17;fontSize=10;fontStyle=0;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;" value="REFERENCE LINEAGE   (FROM CLASS)&lt;br&gt;• Data &amp;amp; Analytics Pipeline (Slide 16)&lt;br&gt; → Storage, Processing, Warehouse / BI&lt;br&gt; (S3 4-Zone, Glue, Athena, Redshift, QuickSight)&lt;br&gt;• ML Pipeline (Slide 17)&lt;br&gt; → MLOps, Monitoring, Drift Loop&lt;br&gt; (SageMaker Pipelines, Monitor, Endpoint)&lt;br&gt;• Customer 360 Extensions (Green)&lt;br&gt; → 7 Internal + 4 External Sources&lt;br&gt; → NLP/ASR (Comprehend, Transcribe)&lt;br&gt; → Feature Store (Online + Offline)&lt;br&gt; → DynamoDB Cache &amp;amp; Agent Activation" vertex="1">
